                    <img src="images/feature2.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Feature 2">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center">Event Planning and RSVP</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Plan and organize events easily with our event management feature. Send invitations and track RSVPs effortlessly.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="images/feature3.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Feature 3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center">Real-time Chat Messaging</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Stay connected with friends through our real-time chat messaging. Send instant messages and stay in touch wherever you are.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
